## 트랜잭션 API

### db_transaction()

```freelang
fn db_transaction(f: Fn() -> Result<T, string>) -> Result<T, string>
```

**사용 예**:
```freelang
let result = db_transaction(|| {
    db_insert("users", { name: "Alice" })?
    db_insert("posts", { title: "Hello" })?
    Ok(true)
})
```

